        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">"As an agent, this platform has been invaluable for connecting with serious buyers."</p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-amber-600">— Dalia F., Alexandria</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">"I leased my commercial property with zero hassle. Great service!"</p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-amber-600">— Ahmed H. Cairo </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CTA SECTION -->
<div class="bg-amber-500 py-16 px-6 text-center text-white">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to find your perfect space?</h2>
  <p class="text-lg mb-6">Sign up and start browsing thousands of verified listings today.</p>
  <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "px-6 py-3 bg-white text-amber-600 font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-md hover:bg-gray-100 transition" %>
